600	/*-------------------------------------------------------------------------
601	 * Function: H5IMunlink_palette
602	 *
603	 * Purpose: This function detaches a palette from an existing image dataset
604	 *
605	 * Return: Success: 0, Failure: -1
606	 *
607	 * Comments:
608	 *  based on HDF5 Image and Palette Specification
609	 *
